-- Fondo Strategico Bids for Ansaldo Energia, Sole Says
-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 2012-09-30T10:07:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-30/fondo-strategico-bids-for-ansaldo-energia-sole-says.html
Fondo Strategico Italiano makes
offer for  Finmeccanica (FNC) ’s Ansaldo Energia to counter Siemens’s
bid, Il Sole 24 Ore reports, without citing anyone.
* Fondo Strategico makes offer for 55% stake owned by
Finmeccaninca with group of Italian entrepreneurs: Sole
* Siemens offers ~EU1.3b for 100% of co. and aims to complete
deal by end of 2012: Sole
* NOTE: Fondo Strategico backed by Italy’s state-controlled
lender Cassa Depositi e Prestiti
* NOTE: Siemens Said Preferred Bidder for Finmeccanica’s Ansaldo
